/*STD *  RPGBASE                                                      *
/*EXI *  TEXT('Midas CB Display mutually excl components')
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  Midas - Close of Business Module                             *
      *                                                               *
      *  CB0430D - Mutually exclusive component enquiry subfile       *
      *                                                               *
